00:10:01,769 --> 00:10:03,037
Hello.

271
00:10:03,103 --> 00:10:05,105
ZOE (OFFSCREEN): What
are you doing?

272
00:10:05,139 --> 00:10:06,607
-I was just--

273
00:10:06,607 --> 00:10:07,875
it's a long story.

274
00:10:07,942 --> 00:10:09,276
-Don't worry, precious.

275
00:10:09,310 --> 00:10:11,111
I'll get to your little
girlfriend soon enough.

276
00:10:11,145 --> 00:10:13,113
No offense, but I'm saving
the best for last.

277
00:10:17,785 --> 00:10:19,119
Dark Vapor.

278
00:10:22,289 --> 00:10:23,157
-Stop it.

279
00:10:23,224 --> 00:10:25,759
-Leave him alone!

280
00:10:25,793 --> 00:10:28,863
-Oh man, this has got
to be a dream.

281
00:10:28,896 --> 00:10:32,800
A really bad dream!

282
00:10:32,800 --> 00:10:33,467
-Stop!

283
00:10:33,534 --> 00:10:35,144
