473
00:20:38,561 --> 00:20:39,528
-Yeah.

474
00:20:39,528 --> 00:20:41,063
I hardly recognize myself.

475
00:20:41,097 --> 00:20:42,231
-Huh?

476
00:20:42,264 --> 00:20:43,666
-I don't feel like
a kid anymore.

477
00:20:43,699 --> 00:20:45,501
I think I finally understand
what being a

478
00:20:45,534 --> 00:20:47,737
Digimon is all about.

479
00:20:47,770 --> 00:20:49,672
We're in for an amazing ride.

480
00:20:49,705 --> 00:20:52,708
All of us.

481
00:20:52,708 --> 00:20:55,411
NARRATOR: Wow, who ever thought
Takuya would be the

482
00:20:55,478 --> 00:20:56,846
responsible one?

